      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2020 sedan in good condition. The exterior shows minor surface wear consistent with normal use, with no significant scratches or dents. The interior has light wear with well-maintained upholstery and trim. Mechanically sound with no known issues.",
